Package: spTReg
Type: Package
Title: Spatio-Temporal Mean and Quantile auto-Regression Models
Version: 0.0.0-5
Date: 2023-10-01
Authors@R: c(
  person("Jorge", "Castillo-Mateo", role = c("aut","cre","cph"), email = "jorgecastillomateo@gmail.com", comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-3859-0248"))
  )
Author: Jorge Castillo-Mateo [aut, cre, cph] (<https://orcid.org/0000-0003-3859-0248>)
Maintainer: Jorge Castillo-Mateo <jorgecastillomateo@gmail.com>
Description: Fits, spatially predicts, and temporaly forecasts space-time 
  autocorrelated data in time with space-time varying slope coefficients, 
  autorregressive coefficients and variances using: 
  (1) Mean regression using Gaussian processes and Gaussian errors,
  (2) Quantile regression using Gaussian processes and asymmetric Laplace errors.
License: GPL (>= 2)
URL: https://github.com/JorgeCastilloMateo/spTReg
